  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting the consolidation of the anti-corruption and justice systems in Mexico by strengthening capabilities for detection and investigation of crime and corruption.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Anti-Corruption &amp; Rule of Law strand of the Mexico programme will contribute to the consolidation of the anti-corruption and justice systems in Mexico by strengthening capabilities for detection and investigation of crime and corruption cases. It will work to improve policy, procedures and standards; build capacity of public officials detecting and investigating crime and corruption cases; and improve inter-institutional coordination between security, justice and anti-corruption institutions. Creating an&#xA0;environment that promotes prosperity for all.&#xA0;This will increase economic growth by attracting investment and contributing to poverty reduction and gender equality. [Following a methodology change, from financial year 19/20 costs under this activity will be reported against a new activity line. You can find the new IATI identifier by looking up &#x201C;other identifier information&#x201D;.]</narrative>
  </description>
